{"tid":2423041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"家長太扯！網購大型弓箭組在家玩　哥哥射中7歲弟右臉險中太陽穴","createTime":"2021-02-25T15:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T16:01:56.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97678162f2ed7d2aee5088efc2a17a24b7a7d8da","tid":2423041,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:46:37.000Z","msg":"南投一名男童在家中空地玩有殺傷力的弓箭，不慎導致一旁7歲弟弟右邊臉頰遭箭矢射中<br />\n，家長看到嚇壞，趕緊將弟弟送醫，醫師施行手術時，發現箭矢已刺入約2.5公分，差點<br />\n刺中眼睛及顏面神經，所幸經拔除後沒有大礙，不過膽戰心驚的畫面已讓家屬嚇壞，趕緊<br />\n把弓箭丟掉，再也不敢讓孩子玩了。<br />\n <br />\n家屬向醫師表示，過年期間帶哥哥（12歲）逛夜市，玩了弓箭射氣球遊戲，之後就吵著也<br />\n要一組，家長只好在網路上購買弓箭組，讓哥哥可以盡情的射箭，沒想到上周五（19日）<br />\n下午，哥哥在自家院子射箭時，弟弟剛好從標靶旁經過，哥哥一時未注意就不小心射中弟<br />\n弟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20210225/HB2JYWWEHVFZFHVRVNNLJGS3DE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20210225%2FHB2JYWWEHVFZFHVRVNNLJGS3DE%2F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd68sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=505b9c73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20210225%2FHB2JYWWEHVFZFHVRVNNLJGS3DE%2F&h=0e6282c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20210225/HB2JYWWEHVFZFHVRVNNLJGS3DE/</a>"},{"pid":"b567691d0bc852a62c20defa1e0153a574e07528","tid":2423041,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"孫伯符<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031b1c09fd347b40b3963e0727bec50b82d8b56f","tid":2423041,"uid":349494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:50:15.000Z","msg":"太陽穴？！不如話頭頂啦"},{"pid":"c6c7e99b8f134ac0ee8e0d9240603d49a7d82516","tid":2423041,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b567691d0bc852a62c20defa1e0153a574e07528","tid":2423041,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"孫伯符<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-